prodNameC: 卡蒂雅TM沙眼披衣菌IgA抗體檢測試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
1.Chlamydia(strain LGV II) antigen coated microassay plate.
2.Serum Diluent Type I.
3.Cutoff calibrator human serum or defibrinated plasma.
4.Control: a)High positive Control b)Low positive control c)Negative control plasma.
5.Horseradish-peroxidase(HRP) Conjugate: Goat anti-human IgA.
6.Chromogen/Substrate Solution Type I: Teramethylbenzidine(TMB).
7.Wash Buffer Type I (20x concentrate): contains TBS, Tween-20 and proclin(0.1%) as preservative.
8.Stop Solution: contains a 1 N H2SO4 solution.
applicantAddr: 新北市板橋區民生路一段三三號六樓之五
efficacy: 檢測人體血液中披衣菌屬抗原抗體IgA。
